cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as word alignment. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The aggregation operation used in the model could also be related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of window representations could suggest a connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
